snippet.textDisplay:
For Deliver Carriables my best method was doing Stella Montis night raids (1,000 per) There are a few shortcut garage doors that can be unlocked in the lobby that take fuel cells, what's really nice about them is that you can deliver a fuel cell from either side of the door so you can effectively do two per door. You can find them in the Central corridors or inside of the lobby, either side really. The lobby is where everyone throws down, a hotly contested PvP area. So just wait until all the fighting or until late-game, whichever comes first and you should have some fuel cells to yourself. Nobody is really doing these in S.M. Night raid because of the huge risk of PVP, but I did it on a free loadout :)

Seed Vault door and Robotic Sandbox (Access Capacitor) also are also another couple of places you can hit to finish off the challenge if you don't get the 4 you need from the lobby.
